# PolicyDhara and DevDiscourses are proxied via Netlify Edge Functions
# (see netlify/edge-functions/policydhara.ts and devdiscourses.ts). We
# can't use _redirects rules here — Netlify's trailing-slash normalisation
# matches the proxy rule on the no-slash form, so the page renders unstyled
# because relative asset paths resolve against the wrong base. The edge
# function injects a <base> tag in the proxied HTML, which fixes that.

